hared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3030800/extras/a561dd08a648f5002edc37da5be1208c.webm?t=1768545824\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3030800/extras/a561dd08a648f5002edc37da5be1208c.mp4?t=1768545824\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Creates a pool of water that the girl can swim inside on it, allowing her to reach some areas.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>3）FIRE Magic Cube</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3030800/extras/480ef230f03509ccc43d7ba3d38b0a52.poster.avif?t=1768545824\" width=1000 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3030800/extras/480ef230f03509ccc43d7ba3d38b0a52.webm?t=1768545824\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3030800/extras/480ef230f03509ccc43d7ba3d38b0a52.mp4?t=1768545824\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Generates flames that can provide the girl upsize, allowing her to move faster Or jump higher to reach high platforms.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>4）WIND Magic Cube</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3030800/extras/829efb60e0c37418bb209ced34dc7505.poster.avif?t=1768545824\" width=1000 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3030800/extras/829efb60e0c37418bb209ced34dc7505.webm?t=1768545824\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai